reviewText: Anyone who loves animes, action, the wild west, a blend of silliness and seriousness, and all around awesomeness, this anime is for you.

I tipically do not buy anime since it can be streamed very easly, but when I compaired the quality of the DVD in this set there is no comparison.

The colors are vibrant and it has been faithfully remastered the english tracks.

However do not look for exstras cause you will be disapointed.
